  "prompt": "What are some of the best Soft Rock songs of all time?",
  "response": "Soft rock, characterized by its smooth melodies and mellow sound, has produced numerous timeless hits over the years. Here are some of the best soft rock songs of all time:\n\n1. \"Hotel California\" \u2013 Eagles\n2. \"Your Song\" \u2013 Elton John\n3. \"Everything I Own\" \u2013 Bread\n4. \"Landslide\" \u2013 Fleetwood Mac\n5. \"Just the Way You Are\" \u2013 Billy Joel\n6. \"Fire and Rain\" \u2013 James Taylor\n7. \"Africa\" \u2013 Toto\n8. \"Sailing\" \u2013 Christopher Cross\n9. \"How Deep Is Your Love\" \u2013 Bee Gees\n10. \"Tiny Dancer\" \u2013 Elton John\n11. \"I Want to Know What Love Is\" \u2013 Foreigner\n12. \"She's Always a Woman\" \u2013 Billy Joel\n13. \"Baby Come Back\" \u2013 Player\n14. \"Alone Again (Naturally)\" \u2013 Gilbert O'Sullivan\n15. \"If You Leave Me Now\" \u2013 Chicago\n16. \"Summer Breeze\" \u2013 Seals & Crofts\n17. \"Babe\" \u2013 Styx\n18. \"Still the One\" \u2013 Orleans\n19. \"Do That to Me One More Time\" \u2013 Captain & Tennille\n20. \"Escape (The Pi\u00f1a Colada Song)\" \u2013 Rupert Holmes\n\nThese songs have not only stood the test of time but continue to evoke strong emotions and memories for listeners around the world.",
